			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="You get a telepathing message from the elder brain if you killed Gortash before killing Orin. This dialog starts right after the combat wil Gortash ends.&#xD;&#xA;If the foundry hasn't been destroyed yet, the brain promises to take care of it.&#xD;&#xA;The brain also rassures the palyer that they will take care of any witnesses to the palyer killing Gortash.&#xD;&#xA;The Brain instructs the palyer to kill Orin." />
